                        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_xpath_functions.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;25:33">http://www.oxygenxml.com/ai/function</codeph>) that can be used
