                <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_xpath_functions.dita" xtrc="p:5;69:20"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_xpath_functions.dita" xtrc="b:19;69:23">Sample Use in Schematron:</b></p>
